News.Title: Pranik Logistics: Muted Market Debut with 2.5% Premium
News.Summary: Pranik Logistics listed on NSE SME at ₹79, a 2.5% premium over its IPO price of ₹77. The ₹22.47 crore IPO was oversubscribed 218.02 times. The company plans to use funds for technology investment, capital expenditure, and working capital needs.
